WEBVTT

00:00:01.756 --> 00:00:03.095
Well, hello.

00:00:04.211 --> 00:00:05.963
This is Sophie.

00:00:05.987 --> 00:00:08.093
It's all right, don't worry,

00:00:08.117 --> 00:00:09.624
everything's going to be fine.

00:00:09.648 --> 00:00:11.558
(Laughter)

00:00:11.582 --> 00:00:15.321
There are some people on the balcony
that are very happy to be up there now.

00:00:15.345 --> 00:00:16.924
(Laughter)

00:00:16.948 --> 00:00:18.574
So this is Sophie --

00:00:18.598 --> 00:00:20.337
not Sophia -- no, Sophie.

00:00:20.361 --> 00:00:21.794
She has a French name.

00:00:21.818 --> 00:00:22.996
And you wonder why?

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:24.024
(Laughter)

00:00:24.048 --> 00:00:28.339
So Sophie, for most people,
is the incarnation of terror, really.

00:00:28.363 --> 00:00:30.475
She's far too leggy, she's far too hairy,